      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Apply qualification standards  agreed upon for this purchasing relationship to each candidate supplier. Attempt to determine the supplier's capability to manufacture and distribute quality product. Which meets company need. Consider QS 9000 Certification, market share, D&amp;B rating. Supplier's production capacity, supplier location, supplier distribution, ability to provide technical support, loyalty to company."/>
